data.description: A rare opportunity to own a custom built, luxurious rental beach home located just over 50 steps to the white sands and emerald waters of Pensacola Beach that boasts water views from all rooms. The homes is fully furnished and could be a turn-key rental with repeat renters.  An open floor plan that includes an all stainless commercial grade kitchen (double oven, ice maker, refrigerator, custom built cabinets) with bar seating, room for a large dining table that flows into a living room that is flooded with natural light and opens to a beautiful covered deck.  Main floor master bedroom with custom full 15' X 15' bathroom. 2nd Master bedroom on upper floor with a full bath and 3rd bedroom has full bath and private balcony. The 4th and 5th bedrooms share a Jack & Jill bathroom. All bathrooms feature stone and granite tops and sinks.  The massive gunite and deco tile private pool(with outdoor heated shower) along with over 6000 sq ft of outdoor living area and deck space with custom landscaping and outdoor lighting will be a great place to entertain family, and perfect for weddings or reunions. Parking for at least 12 vehicles with 5 covered spaces.  A large elevator will take you and anything you need to all three floors.  The beautiful Gulf of Mexico, as well as, most of the island can be seen from the elevated viewing deck. High end windows, doors and insulation package as well as high end tile throughout.  So pack your chairs and umbrella and start enjoying the life you deserve!
